        <image source="images/fig-ans-4-2-17.jpg" alt="two shifts of growth" width="35%"/>
    </p></li>
    <li><p>The graph of <m>f</m> is reflected about the <m>x</m>-axis; the graph of <m>g</m> is reflected about the <m>y</m>-axis.</p></li>
